Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
Enquiry.java This class represents an enquiry made by an applicant regarding a housing project. It contains details such as the applicant's NRIC, project name, message content, and a reply ID. The class provides methods to set and get these details, as well as to check if the enquiry has a reply.
